item.dc:creator: @n0va_k0 n0va k0
item.description:
@n0va_k0 wrote:

You are supposed to go on File>New>Choose Text Document and then open it. After that, hold one of the .cfg files and move it into the blank text document. There you should actually read it. Change whatever you intended to change and save it. Compile. Client.java is the java text document that says client >.>…
